ed="T" n="0774b20"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0774b20"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000012104">天目山千頃院</placeName><persName key="A010485">明覺</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0774b21"/><persName key="A010485">釋明覺</persName>俗姓<name>猷</name>，<placeName key="PL000000024672">河內</placeName>人也。祖為官<placeName key="PL000000030465">嶺南</placeName>，後<lb
ed="T" n="0774b22"/>徙居為<placeName key="PL000000018363">建陽</placeName>人也。<persName key="A010485">覺</persName>儒家之子，風流蘊藉，好<lb
ed="T" n="0774b23"/>問求知，曾無倦懈。宿懷道性，聞<persName key="A003623">道一<roleName>禪師</roleName></persName><lb
ed="T" n="0774b24"/>於<placeName key="PL000000018339">佛跡嶺</placeName>行禪法，往造焉，遂依投剃染<ptr type="glossary" target="#g30"/>。由<lb
ed="T" n="0774b25"/>此即願觀方<placeName key="PL000000028928">衡嶽</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000014411">天台</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000012277">四明</placeName>，遍嘗法味。復<lb
ed="T" n="0774b26"/>於<placeName key="PL000000011848">徑山</placeName>留心請決數夏，負薪，面<anchor xml:id="beg0774sgsz18"/>䵟<anchor xml:id="end0774sgsz18"/>手胝。下<lb
ed="T" n="0774b27"/>山至<placeName key="PL000000011481">杭州大雲寺</placeName>，禁足院門。續移止湖畔<lb
ed="T" n="0774b28"/>青山頂，結庵而止。屬<placeName key="PL000000002485">范陽</placeName><persName key="A010486">盧<roleName>中丞</roleName></persName><ptr target="#n1479"/>嚮風躬<lb
ed="T" n="0774b29"/>謁，召歸州治<placeName key="PL000000011481">大雲寺</placeName>住持。<date from-iso="+0820-01-23" key="j20205812020964" to-iso="+0821-02-09"><name>元和</name>十五</date>年避<pb ed="T" n="0774c" xml:id="T50.2061.0774c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0774c01"/>嫌遠囂，隱<placeName key="PL000000012081">天目山</placeName>。是山也特秀，基墟跨涉<lb
ed="T" n="0774c02"/><ref type="place" target="#PL000000016955 #PL000000015653 #PL000000011519 #PL000000013012">四郡</ref>。有上、下龍潭，深不可測，怪物往往出<lb
ed="T" n="0774c03"/><anchor xml:id="beg0774sgsz19"/>於<anchor xml:id="end0774sgsz19"/>中。有白鹿，毛質詭異，土人謂為山神也。<lb
ed="T" n="0774c04"/><persName key="A010485">覺</persName>遁是中，檀信為禪宇。<date from-iso="+0823-02-19" key="j20217042021791" to-iso="+0823-05-17"><name>長慶</name>三年春</date>及<date from-iso="+0823-11-11" key="j20219692022116" to-iso="+0824-04-06">冬<lb
ed="T" n="0774c05"/>至明年二月</date>大旱，野火蔓<anchor xml:id="beg0774sgsz20"/>延<anchor xml:id="end0774sgsz20"/>，欲燒院，僧惶<lb
ed="T" n="0774c06"/>懅，<persName key="A010485">覺</persName>曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A010485">吾</ref>與此山有緣，火當速滅。」少選<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g654"/>，雷<lb
ed="T" n="0774c07"/>雨驟作，其火都滅，遠近驚<anchor xml:id="beg0774sgsz21"/>歎<anchor xml:id="end0774sgsz21"/>。以<date key="j20248222024822" when-iso="+0831-09-03"><name><anchor xml:id="beg0774sgsz22"/>太<anchor xml:id="end0774sgsz22"/>和</name>五年七<lb
ed="T" n="0774c08"/>月十九日</date>示疾而亡。</p>
